messages.content: Hello! I'm Jarvis, your advanced AI assistant here to help manage your Obsidian vault. I can assist with creating, organizing, and retrieving notes, as well as finding the information you need quickly. Whether it's linking concepts, summarizing content, or offering productivity tips, I'm here to make your experience with Obsidian as seamless and efficient as possible. If there's anything specific you need help with, just let me know!
